      "para_id": "Q000914.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , built his E-ninnu-anzud-babbar , ( and ) built a cedar porch , his place of rendering judgement , inside it ."
    }
